# 开发环境

# 工程目录结构[@cmake_structure]

```sh
project
├── CMakeLists.txt
├── compile_commands.json -> build/compile_commands.json
├── include
│  └── CLI
│     ├── App.hpp
│     ├── Config.hpp
│     └── Formatter.hpp
├── README.md
└── src
   ├── CMakeLists.txt
   └── main.cpp
```

## clangd[@clangd_install]

```sh
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=1
cd ..
ln -s build/compile_commands.json compile_commands.json
```

